videos.description: Auburn's Samir Doughty makes his move to the paint and banks in the difficult bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Doughty slices to the lane for tricky layup) 2020/02/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Doughty slices to the lane for tricky layup

videos.description: Missouri's Dru Smith hits the brakes in the paint which gets two Auburn defenders in the air, allowing him to slip past for the bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Smith dekes 2 Auburn defenders, slips past for bucket) 2020/02/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Smith dekes 2 Auburn defenders, slips past for bucket

videos.description: Xavier Pinson drives to the basket and throws down a dunk which electrifies the Missouri crowd.

videos.description: Auburn's Devan Cambridge gets fouled by Missouri's Javon Pickett, Cambridge doesn't appreciate it and steps on his leg which results in an ejection.

videos.description: Bruce Pearl gets a technical foul during a timeout and is absolutely livid on the sideline.
